03:09.450 --> 03:11.441
And I'm sorry.

03:12.720 --> 03:14.711
I'm so sorry
this is happening to us,

03:14.760 --> 03:16.955
to you.

03:16.990 --> 03:19.697
Mom, that's it?

03:19.730 --> 03:21.755
That's all you're
gonna tell me?

03:24.000 --> 03:25.865
Mom, what did he do?

03:29.610 --> 03:31.601
Your father's been...

03:35.510 --> 03:37.842
paying for prostitutes
on the road,

03:37.880 --> 03:39.973
at least the one
we met With yesterday,

03:40.020 --> 03:41.908
for years.

03:46.490 --> 03:48.879
Then I don't want
to see hIm again.

03:54.630 --> 03:56.495
( sighs )

04:03.070 --> 04:06.233
Okay,
so what happens now?

04:07.410 --> 04:09.378
Where do we live?

04:11.050 --> 04:12.517
Mom, is he
going to jail?

04:12.550 --> 04:14.609
No.

04:14.650 --> 04:16.789
He's not going to jail.

04:18.520 --> 04:20.659
He is a free man.

04:22.060 --> 04:24.620
It's all arranged.
We'll stay here.

04:24.660 --> 04:26.525
At least until the end
of the harvest season.

04:26.560 --> 04:29.028
Yeah, when is that?

04:29.060 --> 04:30.823
Fall.

04:35.440 --> 04:38.261
So, you mean
I'm taking my SATs here?

04:40.110 --> 04:42.544
Going to school here?

04:46.580 --> 04:49.686
