for the next six months.

05:09.100 --> 05:11.807
Ralph Angel:
Hey, Charley,
checking if you're back.

05:11.840 --> 05:14.400
Got a fertilizer delivery
coming in at 10:00.

05:14.440 --> 05:16.544
You need to sign
for it.

05:16.580 --> 05:17.842
Okay?

05:21.150 --> 05:23.448
Here we are.

05:24.720 --> 05:26.813
Scoot that over.

05:26.860 --> 05:28.589
Eat your food.

05:34.160 --> 05:35.991
What we gonna do
today, Pops?

05:36.030 --> 05:37.998
- Work.
- But it's Saturday.

05:38.030 --> 05:39.861
Blue, farmers work
every day.

05:39.900 --> 05:42.437
Then I don't
want to be a farmer.

05:42.470 --> 05:44.006
( chuckles )

05:48.610 --> 05:51.602
- That you and me?
- No, me and Mommy.

05:53.750 --> 05:55.741
When do I get to see
Mommy again?

06:02.760 --> 06:04.387
( knocking )

06:08.630 --> 06:10.495
Now, eat your food.

06:14.040 --> 06:15.132
Hey!

06:15.170 --> 06:17.764
Man, when you said
you had a farm,

06:17.810 --> 06:19.471
you weren't kidding.

06:19.510 --> 06:21.478
