If you called earlier,

06:21.510 --> 06:23.603
I would have tried
to clean up and
whatnot, but--

06:23.650 --> 06:26.517
Oh, well, that defeats
the purpose of a home
visit, right?

06:27.920 --> 06:29.649
Yeah, you right.
Come on.

06:29.690 --> 06:33.148
Blue, say hello
to Mr. Jarvis.

06:33.190 --> 06:35.556
- Hi.
- Hey, little man.

06:36.960 --> 06:39.497
Give me a high five.

06:39.530 --> 06:42.829
- So, what you
drawing there?
- Mommy.

06:45.200 --> 06:47.065
Do you know her?

06:47.100 --> 06:49.807
No, I don't, actually.

06:56.680 --> 06:58.204
But I like what
you're doing, though.

06:58.250 --> 07:00.514
- Thank you.
- Jarvis: You're welcome.

07:00.550 --> 07:03.189
Blue, let's go
brush your teeth.

07:03.220 --> 07:04.915
I'll take you over
to Aunt Violet's

07:04.950 --> 07:07.180
once I'm done
talking to Mr. Jarvis.

07:07.220 --> 07:09.552
Blue:
Okay.

07:09.590 --> 07:10.989
Ralph Angel:
Sorry.

07:12.560 --> 07:14.528
Hey.

07:14.560 --> 07:16.528
Jarvis:
All right.

07:16.570 --> 07:19.789
Come on, take a seat.
I'll get some of this
stuff up here.

07:19.840 --> 07:21.796
It's all good.

07:21.840 --> 07:24.058
All right.

07:24.110 --> 07:25.930
So, Blue has
his own room, huh?

07:25.970 --> 07:27.801
Sure does.
It's big, too.

07:27.840 --> 07:29.102
- Right.
- Mm-hmm.

07:29.140 --> 07:31.244
So, he's not living here
with you, though?

07:31.280 --> 07:34.215
Where else _
he supposed to live?

07:34.250 --> 07:36.582
With his appointed
legal guardian--

07:36.620 --> 07:39.214
your aunt.

07:39.250 --> 07:42.720
My Aunt Vi was only
watching him when
I was inside.

07:45.130 --> 07:48.691
DCFS rule says...

07:48.730 --> 07:50.220
she has custody
for another year.

07:50.270 --> 07:52.090
Why?

07:52.130 --> 07:55.236
I've been out
for seven months without
Violating my parole.

07:55.270 --> 07:57.135
- I got my own place--
- Hey, listen.

07:57.170 --> 07:59.604
You don't have
to convmce me.

07:59.640 --> 08:01.733
Convince your aunt.

08:01.780 --> 08:04.704
Now, if she signs that,

08:04.750 --> 08:07.014
you'll have full custody
of Blue again.

08:12.890 --> 08:14.585
Is Mom back
in the picture?

08:14.620 --> 08:16.759
Hell, no.

08:16.790 --> 08:20.590
She just watched him
one time for the funeral.

08:20.630 --> 08:23.019
Seems to have left
an Impressmn.

08:25.200 --> 08:27.998
- Is she clean now?
- So she say.

08:28.040 --> 08:30.008
Says she got a job
with benefits,

08:30.040 --> 08:32.167
but I don't know.

08:33.640 --> 08:37.144
You know,
speaking of jobs...

08:37.180 --> 08:40.274
you want to tell me
what went down at
the warehouse?

08:40.320 --> 08:42.641
I got laid off.

08:43.790 --> 08:45.746
- I heard.
- Mm-hmm.

08:45.790 --> 08:48.008
You know,
it's funny timing,

08:48.060 --> 08:52.895
'cause I remember you
complaining about that job
before you got laid off.

08:52.930 --> 08:55.148
Right before the bust.
You hear about that?

08:55.200 --> 08:56.929
Nah, what happened?

08:59.100 --> 09:01.295
I know you know something
happened, Ralph Angel,

09:01.340 --> 09:03.160
'cause
the Sheriff's Department
came out here.

09:03.210 --> 09:04.802
And they didn't
find nothing.

09:04.840 --> 09:06.205
Mm.

09:08.080 --> 09:10.048
Well, if you
don't know nothing,

09:10.080 --> 09:12.048
let me fill you in.

09:12.080 --> 09:14.674
The guys
you were working with
was running a racket.

09:14.720 --> 09:18.042
They were stealing
cell phones and laptops.

09:18.090 --> 09:21.480
And now they're looking
at five to 10 years.

09:25.360 --> 09:28.352
So, considering
the circumstances,

09:28.400 --> 09:31.927
I'm not going to
report you because
you're out of a job,

09:31.970 --> 09:35.929
but you're going to
need to find one fast.

09:35.970 --> 09:38.939
I'm gonna work here,
on the farm.

09:38.970 --> 09:42.098
- Got it all worked out.
- ( sighs )

09:42.140 --> 09:44.847
We've gone over this,
Ralph Angel.

09:46.380 --> 09:49.713
You need_
a working busmess
to employ you,

09:49.750 --> 09:51.945
something with a tax ID
and a DBA number.

09:51.990 --> 09:54.686
The farm got all that.
My sister made sure of it.

09:54.720 --> 09:57.120
Okay, so can
your sister make sure
that you get paid

09:57.160 --> 09:59.355
minimum wage
at 40 hours a week,

09:59.390 --> 10:01.950
plus health insurance
and worker's comp?

10:02.000 --> 10:04.218
That's not
gonna be a problem.

10:04.270 --> 10:05.862
Okay.

10:07.270 --> 10:08.862
Okay.

10:11.410 --> 10:14.402
You have her...

10:14.440 --> 10:16.977
do all that you said

10:17.010 --> 10:20.013
and fill that out.

10:20.050 --> 10:22.041
You can work here
for your parole.

