13:00.910 --> 13:03.049
I'm sorry.
I can't leave the tanker
without getting paid.

13:03.080 --> 13:04.877
Well, can you wait
until I call the bank?

13:04.910 --> 13:07.413
Do I have a choice?

13:07.450 --> 13:09.543
Sorry, bro.
Give us a second.

13:09.580 --> 13:10.888
It's all good.

13:10.920 --> 13:13.286
Card declined.

13:13.320 --> 13:15.288
Hi, this is Charlotte
Bordelon-West.

13:15.320 --> 13:18.050
