with these herbs.

13:50.260 --> 13:53.093
( car door slams )

13:53.130 --> 13:55.496
- Just a sec.
- All right.

14:01.500 --> 14:03.468
Charley?

14:03.510 --> 14:05.102
What are you doing here?
What's wrong?

14:05.140 --> 14:07.472
You!
Nova, you're wrong.

14:07.510 --> 14:10.206
