but I had to do something
to help Too Sweet.

14:16.250 --> 14:18.218
And after all
the shit you gave me

14:18.250 --> 14:21.356
whenever I offered
to pay for anything
at Daddy's funeral.

14:21.390 --> 14:23.119
When_ it serves
your Interests,

14:23.160 --> 14:24.479
you have no problem
stealing money from me.

14:24.530 --> 14:26.486
