I fully plan on
returning it.

14:28.530 --> 14:30.225
Taking money
without permission

14:30.270 --> 14:32.226
is the definition
of stealing, Nova.

14:32.270 --> 14:34.135
However you want
to define it, okay.

14:34.170 --> 14:36.365
I am apologizing.

14:36.400 --> 14:37.662
I should have talked
to you about it,

14:37.710 --> 14:40.372
but I'm not sorry
I did it.

14:40.410 --> 14:42.139
What if it had been Micah?

14:42.180 --> 14:44.102
