guilty man.

14:48.020 --> 14:49.647
Don't bring my family
into this

14:49.680 --> 14:51.386
and don't count my money.

14:51.420 --> 14:53.251
Everything cool?

14:53.290 --> 14:55.155
Yeah.
This is my sister.

15:00.460 --> 15:03.918
And don't ever talk
to me about anybody's
"trifling ass."

15:05.030 --> 15:06.292
( scoffs )

