15:51.380 --> 15:53.519
- Mm...
- ( Micah clears throat)

15:56.650 --> 15:59.039
Oh, yeah.
You said you wanted
something, right, Blue?

15:59.090 --> 16:00.751
Yeah.

16:00.790 --> 16:02.314
- Here you go.
- Thank you.

16:02.360 --> 16:04.180
Why don't y'all go
to the ice cream store?

16:04.230 --> 16:06.084
- Ooh, you want to go
get some ice cream?
- Of course.

16:06.130 --> 16:07.324
- "Of course."
- ( all laugh )

16:07.360 --> 16:08.497
Come on, let's go.

16:10.100 --> 16:11.499
Wait... Micah?

16:11.530 --> 16:12.758
You ain't
got to hurry back.

16:12.800 --> 16:15.337
( stammers, scoffs )

16:15.370 --> 16:17.065
Micah:
Hey, slow down,
little man.

16:17.110 --> 16:18.600
Why don't you
help me unpack?

16:18.640 --> 16:21.074
I think we both
got some unpacking
to do.

16:21.110 --> 16:22.338
Yes, we do.

16:22.380 --> 16:24.974
- ( chatter)
- ( sizzling )

16:28.680 --> 16:31.114
- Hey.
- Hey.

16:32.390 --> 16:33.755
Thanks.

16:33.790 --> 16:35.678
Ain't no thing.

16:38.560 --> 16:40.118
So, Nova take the $10,000?

16:40.160 --> 16:42.424
Let's not talk about it.

16:45.130 --> 16:47.769
I told the delivery guy
to come back this afternoon.

16:47.800 --> 16:50.769
Think you can
be there to pay him?

16:50.810 --> 16:53.802
( laughs )
Why not?

16:53.840 --> 16:57.276
