is dispense cash,
apparently.

17:00.550 --> 17:01.778
How can I help you?

17:01.820 --> 17:03.378
I'll have
the crab cake salad.

17:03.420 --> 17:05.411
Corned beef Benny.

17:05.450 --> 17:07.259
Oh, and go easy
on the sauce.

17:07.290 --> 17:09.383
Oh, I'll serve it up
any way you want it,
honey.

17:09.420 --> 17:11.422
( laughing )

