25:31.360 --> 25:32.657
Please?

25:34.660 --> 25:37.322
Well, I mean,
unless you want me
to help with the lights.

25:37.360 --> 25:39.897
I don't know.
Let me think about it.

25:42.070 --> 25:43.662
- You think so?
- Mm.

25:45.670 --> 25:47.774
( laughs )
Nah, I think we can
manage without you.

25:47.810 --> 25:51.177
- ( laughing )
- Y'all go have a good time.

25:51.210 --> 25:53.303
- Nova:
We'll see y'all later.
- Both: All right.

25:53.350 --> 25:55.716
Y'all have a good time.

25:56.980 --> 25:59.187
Ah, ah, no.

25:59.220 --> 26:01.688
- Holleood:
No, you're pulling it, now.
- Okay, you do it!

26:09.400 --> 26:11.322
Mr. Odums?

26:11.370 --> 26:13.668
Hey, peace.
"Bmike" is fine.

26:13.700 --> 26:15.668
Nova Bordelon,
"New Orleans Daily News."

26:15.700 --> 26:17.099
