- Pleasure to meet you,
brother.

26:18.240 --> 26:19.832
Oh, wow.

26:19.870 --> 26:21.679
"I am a man."

26:21.710 --> 26:24.372
But he's
so young here.

26:24.410 --> 26:25.968
Who's that?

26:27.110 --> 26:28.338
I mean, I know...

26:28.380 --> 26:30.348
I know Trayvon Martin,

26:30.380 --> 26:32.086
I know Mike Brown.
But who are the other two?

26:32.120 --> 26:36.113
Okay, so, have you
ever seen the movie
"Fruitvale Station"?

26:36.160 --> 26:37.855
Yeah, yeah, yeah.

26:37.890 --> 26:41.849
Okay, well, that's him.
That's Oscar Grant.

26:41.900 --> 26:43.959
And this is Eric Garner,

26:44.000 --> 26:47.367
the father who was
choked to death
in New York.

26:47.400 --> 26:50.699
