were captured on camera.

26:50.740 --> 26:52.367
"I can't breathe,"

26:52.410 --> 26:55.629
which is a rallying call
to this day.

26:57.010 --> 26:58.978
You ever been?

26:59.010 --> 27:00.978
To a rally? No.

27:01.020 --> 27:03.716
There's all kind of
actions and protests

27:03.750 --> 27:05.115
taking place
in California.

27:05.150 --> 27:06.708
And our comrades
over there?

27:06.750 --> 27:08.149
Yeah,
they don't play.

27:10.420 --> 27:13.719
I just--
I've never been mistreated
by police before.

27:13.760 --> 27:16.251
Or anyone,
for that matter.

27:16.300 --> 27:18.996
I guess it's because
of who my dad is.

27:19.030 --> 27:20.395
Davis West.

27:20.430 --> 27:23.433
It doesn't really
matter who he is.

27:23.470 --> 27:25.404
The question is,
who are you?

27:25.440 --> 27:28.773
- Hm.
