want to be?

27:29.910 --> 27:31.172
- Yeah?
- Okay.

27:31.210 --> 27:32.404
- You know?
- Okay.

27:32.450 --> 27:33.917
All right, okay!

27:33.950 --> 27:36.009
- Don't be scared, now.
- I'm not scared.

27:36.050 --> 27:39.144
Come on, let's go
look at some more art.

27:39.190 --> 27:41.158
I started off speaking
to a small audience.

27:41.190 --> 27:43.010
At least I thought.
I just wanted to speak
to the people

27:43.060 --> 27:44.425
in the communities
I painted In.

27:44.460 --> 27:46.325
I felt like if--

27:46.360 --> 27:50.023
especially post-Katrina--
if these neighborhoods
were sick,

27:50.060 --> 27:52.426
then my art had a way
of providing some type
of healing.

27:52.470 --> 27:55.462
So, I initially thought
it was just those people
on that block,

27:55.500 --> 27:59.038
or on that corner,
or, you know, within
that neighborhood.

27:59.070 --> 28:02.176
