Two!

33:46.450 --> 33:48.782
One, two, three, four!

33:48.820 --> 33:50.685
( music playing )

33:53.430 --> 33:56.024
( chatter)

33:59.430 --> 34:01.534
Hollywood:
Ralph Angel!

34:01.570 --> 34:03.128
( laughing )

34:03.170 --> 34:05.035
What's up, boy?

34:13.580 --> 34:15.810
You're late.

34:15.850 --> 34:19.149
I was taking care
of some things.

34:19.190 --> 34:20.839
Where's Blue?

34:20.890 --> 34:22.812
Sleeping.

34:22.860 --> 34:24.418
He eat?

34:24.460 --> 34:26.451
Of course.
( laughs )

34:26.490 --> 34:28.697
He was outside
playing all day.

34:28.730 --> 34:31.324
About wore himself out.

34:34.600 --> 34:36.591
You want me to make
you a plate?

34:38.740 --> 34:40.469
Yeah.

34:40.510 --> 34:42.478
- Yeah?
- Thank you.

34:42.510 --> 34:44.068
"Thank you."
( chuckles )

34:46.880 --> 34:48.472
- You done with that?
- Yeah.

34:50.880 --> 34:53.087
Something
bothering you?

34:54.890 --> 34:56.585
No, I'm good.

34:56.620 --> 34:58.326
Hollywood:
Hey, Vi, Vi, Vi.

34:58.360 --> 34:59.850
Come on,
let's show them
some moves, baby.

34:59.890 --> 35:02.757
I was gonna make
Ralph Angel a plate.

35:02.800 --> 35:05.325
Say, boy, you better make
your own plate, partner.

35:05.370 --> 35:06.894
- Hey!
- Huh? Huh?

35:06.930 --> 35:08.739
Violet:
No, that's trash, baby.

35:08.770 --> 35:10.192
( laughing )

35:10.240 --> 35:11.764
- Aw, yeah!
- Get it, Wood!

35:11.810 --> 35:13.209
- Yeah!
- Whoo!

35:13.240 --> 35:14.639
Get it!

35:16.510 --> 35:18.478
Remy:
Hey, don't hurt nothing.

35:18.510 --> 35:20.341
I ain't got
no insurance
out here!

35:20.380 --> 35:21.779
Dance floor!

35:21.820 --> 35:25.347
Hollywood:
Come on, this way.
Come on, now!

35:25.390 --> 35:27.779
- Come on with me.
Get my drink.
- Hey! Hey!

35:29.260 --> 35:30.887
Hey!

35:30.920 --> 35:34.356
- Ralph Angel:
You know what it is.
- ( laughing )

35:34.400 --> 35:36.356
Here to eat, eat!
Here to eat!

35:36.400 --> 35:38.527
Here to eat!
It's all I can eat.

35:46.410 --> 35:49.129
( cheering, laughing )

35:51.280 --> 35:54.272
( distant music, laughing )

36:03.820 --> 36:06.425
I was where you are
right now.

36:08.560 --> 36:10.699
When my wife,
Shauna, passed...

36:12.000 --> 36:14.389
I felt like
I wanted to run.

36:14.440 --> 36:16.533
Just--

36:16.570 --> 36:18.936
just pack
it all up and run.

36:18.970 --> 36:20.699
Literally.

36:23.710 --> 36:25.746
You can't outrun it,
though.

36:29.980 --> 36:32.210
I tried.

36:35.320 --> 36:39.279
Pretty soon, I realized
that it would just follow me,
because...

36:39.330 --> 36:41.457
grief wasn't
done with me.

36:43.730 --> 36:45.869
It leaves when it's done.

36:50.900 --> 36:52.731
You're gonna
get through this.

36:55.340 --> 36:57.331
Your husband,
your father.

36:59.010 --> 37:02.446
You just got to
take time to feel
it all.

37:02.480 --> 37:05.313
Don't let it chase you,
just...

37:05.350 --> 37:06.442
sit with it,

37:06.490 --> 37:08.981
listen to it,

37:09.020 --> 37:10.749
respect it.

37:10.790 --> 37:13.350
It's the only way
to survive it.

37:16.030 --> 37:19.625
You got people
that want the best
for you.

37:23.400 --> 37:25.368
But you know that
deep down, right?

37:31.910 --> 37:33.639
Excuse me.

37:39.050 --> 37:41.382
- Hollywood: Go fish!
- Nova: Hey, go fish!

37:41.420 --> 37:44.628
( all laughing )

37:44.660 --> 37:47.379
( car approaching )

37:53.670 --> 37:56.389
Is he here?
Is he here?

37:58.670 --> 37:59.932
Is he here?

37:59.970 --> 38:01.801
- Is he here?
- I don't know.

38:01.840 --> 38:03.671
Is he here?

38:06.080 --> 38:08.640
Is he here?

38:08.680 --> 38:11.649
Are you lost, baby?
You need directions?

38:11.690 --> 38:13.646
Who are you looking for,
sweetheart?

38:13.690 --> 38:16.284
Hollywood!
I've been calling him
all day.

38:18.430 --> 38:21.922
Hollywood,
what's she saying?
She say your name.

38:21.960 --> 38:24.053
Vi, this is my ex-wife.

38:24.100 --> 38:25.920
Wife!

38:25.970 --> 38:28.791
Don't you lie to her, Hollywood.
Don't you lie to her.

38:28.840 --> 38:31.400
We still married.

38:31.440 --> 38:33.965
( crying )
We still married.

38:34.010 --> 38:36.934
I don't know.
I don't know
where my baby is.

38:36.980 --> 38:39.676
Hollywood,
I can't find our baby.
I don't know where she is.

38:39.710 --> 38:42.577
It's okay, Leanne.
Leanne, she's safe.

38:42.620 --> 38:45.316
Wh-what baby?
I-I don't understand.

38:47.120 --> 38:49.418
We still Hollywood
and Leanne.
( sobbing )

38:49.460 --> 38:51.553
Hollywood, you better
start explaining.

38:51.590 --> 38:53.558
You should have
stayed with me,
Hollywood.

38:55.860 --> 38:58.829
Why didn't you stay with me?
We could have found our baby.

38:58.870 --> 39:00.428
Why didn't you stay?

39:00.470 --> 39:02.097
You have a child
with her?

39:02.140 --> 39:05.439
No, no.
The first year
that we were married

39:05.470 --> 39:08.132
she got pregnant
and had a miscarriage.

39:08.170 --> 39:10.832
- No!
- It's gonna be okay.
It's gonna be all right.

39:10.880 --> 39:13.440
No! It's not.
( mutters )

39:13.480 --> 39:16.449
Do you have your medication?
Is it in your purse?

39:16.480 --> 39:18.141
- Don't you touch him!
- No, don't, Vi!

39:18.180 --> 39:21.616
- Wait, wait, wait.
- Vi, Vi, she's bipolar.

39:21.660 --> 39:23.013
She needs her medication.

39:23.060 --> 39:25.984
She's got no business
putting her hands on you.

39:26.030 --> 39:29.591
We have every business.
We have every business.

39:29.630 --> 39:31.120
How long we been married,
Hollywood?

39:31.160 --> 39:33.594
How long?
Tell her.

39:33.630 --> 39:37.760
Sh_e needed
the insurance.

39:37.800 --> 39:40.769
She would have lost it
if we divorced proper.

39:43.040 --> 39:44.871
It's gonna be okay,
all right?

39:44.910 --> 39:47.640
I'm gonna take you back home.
You're gonna be fine.

39:49.520 --> 39:54.617
I'm just gonna take her
back to Baton Rouge.

39:54.660 --> 39:56.616
They'll know what to do
at the hospital.

39:56.660 --> 39:58.389
Hollywood...

40:02.560 --> 40:06.667
this whole time
you been back in
Baton Rouge?

40:10.940 --> 40:13.067
Answer me.

40:13.110 --> 40:16.898
When I got back,

40:16.940 --> 40:20.774
I went to see her
for two days.

40:20.810 --> 40:24.075
The hospital calls
because I'm the only
contact.

40:24.120 --> 40:25.815
( Leanne crying )

40:31.690 --> 40:34.557
So, every day

40:34.600 --> 40:36.420
you've been gone...

40:37.700 --> 40:39.429
you've been lying to me.

40:44.270 --> 40:47.205
- So we can--
- Every damn day.

40:47.240 --> 40:51.199
We can talk
about this, chre,
when I get back.

40:51.240 --> 40:53.674
No.

40:53.710 --> 40:55.712
Ain't no need
for you to come back.

41:02.020 --> 41:04.215
You don't mean that,
Violet.

41:04.260 --> 41:06.455
You just go on, now.

41:13.030 --> 41:14.122
Go.

41:16.170 --> 41:18.764
- Go.
- ( sighs )

41:25.750 --> 41:28.719
(voice breaks )
You follow me back
with the truck.

41:28.750 --> 41:30.741
Yeah, I got you.

41:37.160 --> 41:39.253
Don't worry, Hollywood.

41:39.290 --> 41:40.928
I got Aunt Vi.

41:42.300 --> 41:44.256
Okay.

41:44.300 --> 41:46.894
( sobbing )

41:48.770 --> 41:50.169
( Hollywood sobs )

41:59.950 --> 42:02.646
- ( car door closes )
- ( engine starts )

42:04.050 --> 42:05.642
( car door closes )

42:07.050 --> 42:08.813
( car engine starts )

42:35.820 --> 42:38.687
( music playing )
